Four KFC employees were caught defrosting chicken using a hose pipe in a parking lot in Joburg.According to the eyewitnesses the chicken was placed on a garbage bag and a hose pipe was used to defrost the chicken while the employees lean against the wall enjoying the morning sun and smoking cigarettes.Our source said he asked them why they were doing something that was obviously illegal and they told him some of the equipment inside are not working and it s cold inside. I TRIED CHALLENGING THEM AND THEY SAID THIS IS NOTHING IF YOU TAKE A WALK INSIDE YOU WILL VOMIT AND SOME RESTAURANTS ARE WORSE, IF YOU ARE THAT CLEAN COOK YOUR OWN FOOD Our source said he reported the matter to KFC in Gauteng and they said they will investigate and he will be the first to know of what will transpire.